        <h2>From Monroe to the Bronx to Brooklyn to Manhattan</h2>
        <figure style="text-align: center;">
        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT49CDH_RC0HmWVt8D32YsfIJ-Z9Yrqzf3rbg&s" width="100%" alt="Main synagogue in the village of Kiryas joal"><figcaption>Main synagogue in the village of Kiryas Joel</figcaption>
